Subject: [PATCH 06/16] feat(02-01): rebrand Localizable.xcstrings from
 Meshtastic to Pangea

- 19 keys renamed from Meshtastic to Pangea equivalents
- 80 translation values updated across 11 locales
- meshtastic.org URLs replaced with pangea.org (1 key, 8 values)
- 9 Serbian Cyrillic transliterations replaced with Latin Pangea
- Idempotency verified (--check exits 0, byte-identical on re-run)
